cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

The paper discusses the learnability of neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and systems and control (cs.SY). Given that the paper focuses on the learnability of neural networks, cs.LG and cs.NE are the most likely sub-categories. However, since the paper also discusses the application of neural networks in memorization and learning of certain kernel spaces, cs.AI and cs.SY are also likely sub-categories. Finally, since the paper mentions the use of neural networks in computer vision, cs.CV is also a possible sub-category.
